.name
Popper
.author
Pierre Dak Baillargeon 
.version
1.1
.description
Replaces Intuition menus with popup menus which appear under the mouse
pointer instead of in the top of the screen.  You can also "rip" menus from
the menu-bar and keep them on the screen as a window all the time (or close
them with the close gadget, of course).  
